338
00:27:33.375 --> 00:27:36.541
- Please... don't do it.
- Help.

339
00:27:36.625 --> 00:27:38.250
There's no stopping it now.

340
00:27:38.333 --> 00:27:40.250
The tech works.

341
00:27:40.333 --> 00:27:41.625
